name: graphql-renamed
schema:
# weather schema
type Weather {
  id: ID!
  zip: String!
  cityName: String!
  longitude: Float!
  latitude: Float!
  currentWeather: CurrentWeather!
  sunrise: String!
  sunset: String!
}
type CurrentWeather {
  status: String!
  description: String!
  temp: Float!
  feels_like: Float!
  tempHigh: Float!
  tempLow: Float!
  pressure: Int!
  humidity: Int!
  windSpeed: Float!
}
# queries
type Query {
  weather(city: String!): Weather
}
